item.title: Warm Wishes and Cheers: A Festive Message from Joe Menninger
item.description: Dear Esteemed Listeners, As the holiday season wraps us in its joyful embrace, I wanted to take a moment to extend my heartfelt gratitude to each and every one of you who has been a part of our incredible journey here at Startuprad.io. This time of year is not just about the twinkling lights and merry melodies; it's about cherishing connections, celebrating accomplishments, and embracing the spirit of togetherness... Feed: https://fintechgermany.podcaster.de/fintechgermany.rss

item.title: Tunes from Turtle Island S04E52
item.description: Indigenous made Punk, Indie, Rock, Blues, Classical, Soul, Hip Hop, Pop, Rez Metal, and Electronic, by music makers from the Piipaash, Quechan, Northern Cheyenne, Blackfeet, Iñupiaq, Métis, Inuk, Lakota, Nisenan, Cree, and Washoe nations. Brought to you by Tunes From Turtle Island and Pantheon Podcasts. Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/turtleisland
